$ bash - variables

→ Linux/shell/bash/variables/internal

→ Linux/shell/bash/variables/array

sa:

  → Linux/shell/bash

  → Linux/shell/bash/expansion/shell-parameter[Shell parameter expansion], apparently also known as *variable mangling*.

  → Linux/shell/bash/variables/regular-expressions[regular expressions]

  The  bash → Linux/shell/bash/built-in[built in] → Linux/shell/bash/built-in/read[`read`] to assign values to variables from standard in.
